sources.description: A Respectable Family Yek Khanévadéh-e Mohtaram Directed by Massoud Bakhshi Iran, France, 2012 Drama     91 Synopsis Arash is drawn into a series of domestic and financial dramas and he is reminded of the hardships of his childhood at the start of the Iran-Iraq War in 1981.
